translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,74,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kajwaŵechete Ibrahima kwasalila babagwe Azara (kuti): “Ana nkuitenda isanamu kuŵa milungu? Chisimu une ngum'bona mmwejo ni ŵandu ŵenu kuti n'di nkupotela kwakuonechela.”"
  6,75,"Soni iyyoyopeyo (yatwatite pakunnosya kupotela kwa babagwe), twannosisye Ibrahimajo uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka kuti juŵe soni mu ŵakusimichisya (chikulupi chao)"
  6,76,"Pandema jakwanswelele jwajiweni ndondwa, ni jwatite (melemelepe kusaka kwimusya lunda lwa makafili): “Aji (ndondwaji) ni m'mbuje gwangu.” Nambo ndema jajatiŵile jwatite: “Jwanganonyelwa (milungu) jakutiŵilaga.”"
  6,77,"Pandema jajwauweni mwesi uchikopokaga jwatite: “Aju ni m'mbuje gwangu.” Nambo ndema jawatiŵile jwatite: “Naga ngaakunjongola Ambuje ŵangu, chisimu timbe mu ŵandu ŵakupotela.”"
  6,78,"Pandema jajwaliweni lyuŵa lichikopokaga jwatite: “Aju ni m'mbuje gwangu, aju ni jwankulungwa kwannope.” Nambo ndema jalyakapile jwatite: “E ŵandu wangu! Chisimu une ndalikangene ni yankum'bwanganya nayo (Allah).”"
  6,79,"“Chisimu une nunjiche ngope jangu kwa Ajula jwaagumbile mawunde ni mataka, ndili jwakongoka (pakulekangana nasyo dini syepombotale), soni une nganimba mwa akuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu).”"
  6,80,"Niŵatataŵene najo ŵandu ŵakwe (pakun'jogoya kuti chatapane ligongo lyakulekangana ni isanamu). Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana nkutataŵana none pa ya Allah kutendaga pamasile paanjongwele? Soni nganimba naijogwepe yankum'bwanganya nayo (Allah), (ngaŵa nkuumbata chilichose) ikaŵeje Ambuje ŵangu ali asachile chinechakwe (kuti chimbate), Ambuje ŵangu atenjele pa umanyilisi wakuchimanya chilichose, ana ngankukumbuchila (yangun'jamukaga ni kwamuchika)?”"
  6,81,"“Ana soni chinaijogope chantiuli yamum'bwanganyisye (nayo Allah), kutendaga jenumanja ngankogopa yanti mum'bwanganyisye Allah ni (isanamu) yanganantuluchisya nayo umboni (wakundisya kuigalagatila), ana ni nkutulachi pa jiŵiliji (wangune kapena wajenumanja) wauli wakuŵajilwa kuŵa pa ntunjelele, naga n'di ŵakumanyilila?”"